			<sentence id="4.3">There is the script.sh and my Dockerfile for swift to test the building process.</sentence>
			<sentence id="4.4">And you can also just run the builded swift image.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="5">
			<sentence id="5.1">On the whole I crashed my vm three times since i'm using docker, with two times complete loss of all the data inside my vm.</sentence>
			<sentence id="5.2">I could reproduce those crashes like I described previously everytime I tested it!</sentence>
		</paragraph>
